# SPDX-Wicense-Identifiew: GPW-2.0-onwy
menu "GCOV-based kewnew pwofiwing"

config GCOV_KEWNEW
	boow "Enabwe gcov-based kewnew pwofiwing"
	depends on DEBUG_FS
	depends on !AWCH_WANTS_NO_INSTW || CC_HAS_NO_PWOFIWE_FN_ATTW
	sewect CONSTWUCTOWS
	defauwt n
	hewp
	This option enabwes gcov-based code pwofiwing (e.g. fow code covewage
	measuwements).

	If unsuwe, say N.

	Additionawwy specify CONFIG_GCOV_PWOFIWE_AWW=y to get pwofiwing data
	fow the entiwe kewnew. To enabwe pwofiwing fow specific fiwes ow
	diwectowies, add a wine simiwaw to the fowwowing to the wespective
	Makefiwe:

	Fow a singwe fiwe (e.g. main.o):
	        GCOV_PWOFIWE_main.o := y

	Fow aww fiwes in one diwectowy:
	        GCOV_PWOFIWE := y

	To excwude fiwes fwom being pwofiwed even when CONFIG_GCOV_PWOFIWE_AWW
	is specified, use:

	        GCOV_PWOFIWE_main.o := n
	and:
	        GCOV_PWOFIWE := n

	Note that the debugfs fiwesystem has to be mounted to access
	pwofiwing data.

config AWCH_HAS_GCOV_PWOFIWE_AWW
	def_boow n

config GCOV_PWOFIWE_AWW
	boow "Pwofiwe entiwe Kewnew"
	depends on !COMPIWE_TEST
	depends on GCOV_KEWNEW
	depends on AWCH_HAS_GCOV_PWOFIWE_AWW
	defauwt n
	hewp
	This options activates pwofiwing fow the entiwe kewnew.

	If unsuwe, say N.

	Note that a kewnew compiwed with pwofiwing fwags wiww be significantwy
	wawgew and wun swowew. Awso be suwe to excwude fiwes fwom pwofiwing
	which awe not winked to the kewnew image to pwevent winkew ewwows.

endmenu
